oore spent  years in commercial banking with crestar bank citibank and first bank of new orleans where he was president and ceo for three years mr moore holds an mba with honors from loyola university and a bs in management from tulane university mr moore currently serves as a member of the board of visitors for loyola’s college of business administration bob goodridge general counsel • bethesda md • rgoodridgemidcapfinancialcom •  bob goodridge is midcap’s general counsel prior to joining midcap mr goodridge led the legal teams for merrill lynch capital’s and ge capital’s healthcare finance units mr goodridge has also worked as senior counsel for heller healthcare finance where he led the ucc revised article  conversion efforts and was a partner specializing in finance real estate and corporate law in various law firms mr goodridge was also senior counsel for the st paul insurance cos life insurance business unit where he authored and worked with the maryland legislature to adopt modernized investment laws for life insurance companies mr goodridge holds a jd with high honors from george washington university and was a member of the george washington university law review mr goodridge also holds a bs in finance from the university of virginia randall feldner managing director – finance and accounting • bethesda md • rfeldnermidcapfinancialcom •  randy feldner is midcap’s chief accounting officer and assistant treasurer prior to joining midcap mr feldner held a senior accounting and reporting position at sallie mae inc mr feldner also worked for nine years in public accounting working first for arthur andersen llp then ernst  young llp where he specialized in assurance services in both the financial services and real estate industries mr feldner holds an bba in accounting from the university of richmond and is a certified public accountant in the state of virginia people  apollo capital management lp  howard widra partner • bethesda md • hwidraapollolpcom •  howard w